cs.ET, cs.OH, cs.IT, cs.SI, cs.PL

The paper discusses the use of optical computing for real-time and parallel data processing, which falls under the category of cs.ET (Emerging Technologies). The paper also mentions the use of metamaterial-based analog computing, which could be classified under cs.OH (Other Computer Science). The paper involves mathematical operations and signal processing, which could be categorized under cs.IT (Information Theory) and cs.SI (Signal Processing). Finally, the paper proposes a new method for optical computing, which could be classified under cs.PL (Programming Languages).
